So just a thought, but just because some theme has been done before doesn't mean that it can't be done in a be and interesting way. Most stories you see, read, or hear - for example - wind up being some derivation of a hero's journey. Similarly, there are more apocalypse stories, space disaster stories, and Lovecraftian horror stories than you can shake a stick at.
